{"tid":994690,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"|Switch/3DS機主討論(110)| 2月1號前換領大亂鬥食人花 |","createTime":"2019-01-25T01:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T01:37:36.000Z","uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"472a8380fe73bc0e4e002363026c4c7103dd0a90","tid":994690,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:32:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>食人花換領方法</strong></span>: 去香港eShop入行版食人花code <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>或</strong></span> Switch 主頁對住大亂鬥撳 +掣 &gt; My Nintendo Rewards, 拎完金幣後過一排會收到email拎code, 去返相應你Nintendo Account嘅eShop換領<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  頭post包含 <span style=\"color: gold;\">Q&amp;A</span> / <span style=\"color: orange;\">實用資訊</span> / <span style=\"color: gold;\">遊戲發售表</span>, 請多加善用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/xqr3LCfb/v1074002259-f46c3w132.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fxqr3LCfb%2Fv1074002259-f46c3w132.png&h=8e18177f&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span></span></div><br />\n <br />\nQ: Switch有無鎖區?<br />\nA: 無，eShop 分區跟 ac，一機可同時登入 8 個 ac <br />\n<br />\nQ: 網絡對戰遊戲online玩唔到?<br />\nA: 港服未開, 去<a href=\"https://accounts.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.nintendo.com&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d5ef229b\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.nintendo.com</a>轉region做日本/美國<br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon 連接有問題/ 用用下無反應?<br />\nA: 可以試下撳實JoyCon側邊個Sync掣2秒<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點揀叉電器/USB-C 線?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5oXEONa.png&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=6d7313da\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon手帶調轉插點算?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7bfhKo7dqIo&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=dbcd3cc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連 5gHz WiFi?<br />\nA: Set 個WiFi Channel去36-64 or 100-140之間<br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連大學WiFi?<br />\nA: 連唔到<br />\n<br />\nQ: 部機黑畫面/定咗格/撳電源掣冇反應<br />\nA: 長撳開關掣十二秒<br />\n <br />\nQ: 要keep咩先有保養?<br />\nA: 1. 需維修的主機及配件 2. 主機外箱　 3. 印有銷售店舖名稱或蓋印之購買收據　4. 主機包裝內之香港原裝行貨保固證 <a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9dc01237\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a><br />\n<br />\nQ: Switch行版/日版/美版有咩分別?<br />\nA: 行版有保養同香港用嘅三腳火牛(不過任何版本都係用國際牛)，其他一樣，內置多國語言(無中文)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Nintendo Switch</strong></span> 2017年3月3日 於香港正式發售<br />\n售價 港幣$2,340<br />\n<br />\n任天堂Switch香港官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2F&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b4e25c6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連登post(109)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/975401/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/975401/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch Online App開放下載 (香港未有)</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg&h=467237b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApp功能<br />\n1.同唔同遊戲會有連動要素, 例如Splatoon2, 透過個app可以睇到自己嘅對戰相關數據同買裝<br />\n2. 可以進行語音通話<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg&h=91a4ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch ONLINE會員服務<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>2018年9月19日</strong></span>開始收費<br />\n可享有7日試用期 </span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DcowGUlU0AAFdUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDcowGUlU0AAFdUD.jpg&h=fa2640fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nintendo.com/switch/online-service/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com%2Fswitch%2Fonline-service%2F&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=20f3ac55\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nintendo.com/switch/online-service/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">1. 網絡連線<br />\n<blockquote>成為收費會員後即可在Splatoon, Mario Kart等遊戲中享受網絡對戰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2. NES - Nintendo Switch Online<br />\n<blockquote>(類似Netflix)成為收費會員後即可享受20款<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>追加網絡連線功能</strong></span>嘅NES經典作品, 會定期追加新遊戲 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3. Cloud Save<br />\n<blockquote>成為收費會員後可備份存檔至雲端網絡, 部分遊戲為保公平(官方講法)並不對應cloud save </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n4. Switch Online App<br />\n<blockquote> 連動電話app </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5. 特別優惠<br />\n<blockquote>成為收費會員後可享受不同優惠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n收費: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每年</span> 19.99USD/ 2400YEN (<span style=\"color: red;\">約港幣$160</span>)<br />\n可只購買1或3個月會員資格, 惟其價格亦較昂貴<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Nintendo Switch家長監護程式</span></strong></span><br />\n*裝左可以睇返自已玩左幾耐<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C8nGrvGXkAAhyFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC8nGrvGXkAAhyFV.jpg&h=b021040c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAndroid:<a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nintendo.znma&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2c01e297\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znma</a><br />\niOS:<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1190074407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fid1190074407&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=b6c99692\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1190074407</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂會員 - MyNintendo</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://my.nintendo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy.nintendo.com%2F&d=4wHvwn0c8GG2%2BJennq%2Fg3C7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=872296ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://my.nintendo.com/</a>"},{"pid":"06a2e5ae054dda9b5352473447bcacf7376c6763","tid":994690,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T01:37:36.000Z","msg":"因應時差&amp;為免引起誤會 決定改標題<br />\n請移步去新post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/994696/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/994696/page/1</a>"}]}